entry.title: SUMMER MIX #4 by the pool üåûüí¶

media:group.media:title: SUMMER MIX #4 by the pool üåûüí¶
media:group.media:description:
[NOT REALLY A STUDY MIX, MORE INFO + TRACKLIST IN THE DESCRIPTION]
Hey everyone! We are so happy to finally bring new content to this channel. This is not really a study mix, this is a summer mix (the 4th one!). For those of you that don't know the concept, our summer mixes are made to show you new music that we love and that actually contain lyrics (unlike part of our study mixes, we understand that lyrics don't really help to focus).
We also tried this "Boiler Room" format during a small pool party that I (the younger brother of the two brothers who manage EnjoyStudying) had with some friends. We really hope you'll like it, it was a lot of fun to do :)
So listen to this mix after a day of work, studying, chilling, alone, with friends or family, near the pool, at the beach, at the mountain, wherever you are! Just enjoy the good vibes and we really hope that some of the songs of this mix will be saved in your playlists!
We haven't been posting new content for a while and we are sorry about that. Our DJ Controller broke and we recently bought a new one, let's hope that we will be able to post some mixes during this year (Youtube's Copyright Policy also doesn't really help).
Don't hesitate to tell us which songs you liked and stay safe during this weird 2020 year :)
The EnjoyStudying Team
